Will yield to see if any others would like to weigh in on this.

LGTM, already tested the published RC and the tests are all ✅ 
Welcome Turborepo!

@danielweinmann I'll point out couple lines I had to change in the actual lib code before we merge this huge PR ;)

I like it! Then I can use a pattern I'm used to - which I call: "let zod handle the params"

```ts
export async function action({ request, params }: ActionArgs) {
  return formAction({
    request,
    mutation,
    schema,
    additionalInput: params,
  })
}
```

That said I'm not sure about the naming... it feels to me we could come up with some better name but I'm out of ideas right now 😅

